---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout locale="en" title="Privacy Policy">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <h2>Data Collected</h2>
    <p>This site does not directly collect personal data. Third-party services (Google AdSense, Google Analytics) may collect browsing data under their own privacy policies.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>Advertising cookies may be placed by Google AdSense to display personalized ads. You can disable advertising cookies through your browser settings or the Google consent manager.</p>

    <h2>Advertising</h2>
    <p>This site uses Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google may use cookies to show ads based on your prior visits to this or other websites.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
    <p>Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the right to access, correct, and delete your data. To exercise these rights, contact us at: <a href="mailto:contact@coloriages.example.com">contact@coloriages.example.com</a></p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions about this privacy policy: <a href="mailto:contact@coloriages.example.com">contact@coloriages.example.com</a></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .legal-page h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }

  .legal-page p {
    color: #4b5563;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
